 Chrissy Teigen Tv personality Chrissy Teigen breaks down in tearful clip following a therapy session as she ‘seeks intensive grief counselling after loss of her baby Jack when she suffered a miscarriage. She showed her tear-stained face in the video, which she said was her ‘post-therapy filter’ while holidaying in St. Barts with her family. Chrissy, who shares children Luna and Miles with husband John Legend, has sought grief counselling following a difficult few months.  Chrissy Teigen Breaks Down In Tearful Clip Following A Therapy Session